..TEXT:
|villanello~: The diminutive suffix -^ello~
introduces a modification of sentiment that is essentially
pastoral.  See "pecorelle," vs. 15.  For the whole scene, see
Orosius, ^Hist.~ IV, preface, 7.
..TEXT:
